WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.820 --> 00:00:06.200
focus on food kind not on food amount

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:10.290
you might think that eating little is the
way to weight loss, but you have to know that

00:00:10.290 --> 00:00:12.190
food kind is more important.

00:00:12.190 --> 00:00:17.060
eating a lot of fruits and healthy food is
better than a small amount of bad food.

00:00:17.060 --> 00:00:20.050
Don't leave yourself hungry

00:00:20.050 --> 00:00:24.930
leaving yourself hungry will make fat consumption
too slow, plus you will feel tired.

00:00:24.930 --> 00:00:30.000
so, When you feel hungry, eat fruits or any
healthy food

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.140
replace sweets with fruits

00:00:32.140 --> 00:00:37.149
your body needs sugar, but you can replace
sweets sugar with fruits

00:00:37.149 --> 00:00:41.039
eating a lot before sleep is the worst thing

00:00:41.039 --> 00:00:45.520
worst thing you can do is eating meals before
you sleep, because this meal will be convert

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:50.109
into fat, plus it will not make you sleep
good

00:00:50.109 --> 00:00:52.070
don't exercise and you're hungry

00:00:52.070 --> 00:00:57.280
you might think that doing exercises while
you are hungry will make you lose more fat,

00:00:57.280 --> 00:01:02.410
but the truth is doing this will make you
feel tired, plus you can't exercise well.

00:01:02.410 --> 00:01:05.309
you need energy for your exercises

00:01:05.309 --> 00:01:07.780
try to burn fat everytime you can

00:01:07.780 --> 00:01:10.520
Instead of using elevator, use the stairs.

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:13.610
or try to walk instead of using car

00:01:13.610 --> 00:01:16.479
do not cut down fat or sugar, but reduce it

00:01:16.479 --> 00:01:21.210
cutting down fat or sugar is not a good way
to lose weight, but you have to reduce it

00:01:21.210 --> 00:01:23.430
in order to healthy weight lose

00:01:23.430 --> 00:01:25.340
drink a lot of water

00:01:25.340 --> 00:01:29.549
drinking water as much you can will make you
lose weight too fast.

00:01:29.549 --> 00:01:32.240
you have to drink at least half a gallon per
day

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:35.310
good fats help you to loss weight

00:01:35.310 --> 00:01:41.189
there is two types of fat: bad fat and good
fat, you must reduce bad fat but you have

00:01:41.189 --> 00:01:47.930
to eat more good fat like Olive oil and salmon
to make weight loss effective

00:01:47.930 --> 00:01:53.770
you have to do two things: 1- reduce fat and
sugar, 2- do exercises.

00:01:53.770 --> 00:01:57.020
you must do both of them in order to have
an effective weight loss

00:01:57.020 --> 00:02:04.009
finally, If you followed our tips, you will
have very fast weight loss, try it

